  <brief_title>A Randomized, Double-Blind, Multicenter Study to Evaluate the Acid-inhibitory and Dose-response Efficacy of TAK-438 (20 mg, 40 mg) in Patients With Proton Pump Inhibitor (PPI) - Resistant Erosive Esophagitis</brief_title>
