  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to evaluate the acid-inhibitory and dose-response efficacy of
      TAK-438 (20 mg, 40 mg) in patients with PPI-resistant erosive esophagitis.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
